data.description: **VA ASSUMABLE LOAN 5.25% AVAILABLE!!** Embrace elegance in this fully renovated 5 bed 3 bath estate style home in Roanoke subdivision! This property is zoned for Rossview schools, minutes from shopping & Exit 8! Boasting a gorgeous modern rustic color palette this home features high end light fixtures, refinished hardwood floors, new paint, new HVACS, sit in/office area, formal dining, double ovens, granites throughout, open concept floor plan, huge rec room which could be used as a 6th bedroom, Trex Composite walk out balcony, built-in tesla charger and more! The master bedroom is large with high vaulted ceilings and a ensuite that features double vanities, walk in shower, jet tub, and walk in closet! Entertain you guests in the private back yard which features a huge covered deck which is also made with Trex Composite decking! This luxurious home will not last long on market especially with a 5.25% VA assumable loan option! Lets get a deal done! Schedule your showing today!
